{
  "texts": [
    "And we optimize the calculation of self-attention to avoid too many matrix operations. 2.",
    "We have proposed a new method of attention calculation which is called conv-attention, and apply it in Swin Transformer.",
    "Ps can be reduced by an average of 15.8%, and Params can be reduced by an average of 16%. 3.",
    "The Extension experiment shows that when YOLOX is used as the detection head, the Swin Transformer with conv attention performs better in vehicle target detection.",
    "On the infrared FILR dataset, the MAP is improved by 2.46%."
  ]
}